Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.83,0:23:54.83,*Default,NTP,0050,0000,0000,,{\3c&H00B000A6&\fnMicrosoft Yahei\bord5\an4\fs46}野\N木\N城\N高\N中\N的\N近\N江\N步\N美
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.83,0:24:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0050,0000,,{\3c&H00B000A6&\fnMicrosoft Yahei\bord5\an6\fs46}參\N加\N聯\N合\N觀\N測\N會\N的\N蒼\N榮\N天\N文\N社
